headline: Agoda Joins as Main Sponsor of Singapore's Iconic #HuntTheMouse Cash Hunt
summary: Digital travel platform Agoda has signed up as a main sponsor for the much-anticipated #HuntTheMouse cash hunt in Singapore. Running from 16 October to 14 December 2025, the event is organized by Singaporean company Sqkii and offers participants a chance to win a share of S$1 million by discovering over 600 hidden coins across the island.
